{"tid":297312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗大欖郊野公園　單車女子失控炒車送院死亡","createTime":"2017-06-25T10:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T04:41:16.000Z","uid":19552,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"328047db6445d76b15127e23c0aab343342f63c3","tid":297312,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"下午2時許，1名57歲女子與丈夫及友人,一行７人踩單車遊元朗大欖郊野公園，但途至大棠近麥理浩徑第10段附近，女子踩單車落斜時，突然大叫「煞唔到車！」其後單車連人一同撞向左邊山坡，女子昏迷在地沒有反應，丈夫及友人報警，救護員將女子送往博愛醫院搶救後，證實死亡，初步認為事件無可疑，警方事後檢走有關單車檢驗，了解意外原因。據悉，肇事女子出事時有戴頭盔。"},{"pid":"0832ee24900114ed60654480f06031515f1eefc0","tid":297312,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"有冇可能跳車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674012708095d4305d46d0724fcf67b0425a908e","tid":297312,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"....咁易死"},{"pid":"782b60658baed8c03b563564b74702795b0ef7bf","tid":297312,"uid":79171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"⋯"},{"pid":"31b66a36444f3dc56130cf4baad82185bbcfb008","tid":297312,"uid":14739,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"單車L <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e6db5d56e4c6b72e30fe725a85c49fb223b14f","tid":297312,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1264d76107358d5f5238cccfa1a484330ce68ce","tid":297312,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"呢排自己都踩開單車<br />\n睇到呢d新聞都好唔開心"},{"pid":"6c642740c45b502aa308a8668a5e6b8f5bc56dcd","tid":297312,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislik